SELECT title,name,address
FROM (((library.tbl_library_branch natural join library.tbl_book_loans) Natural jtbl_book_loansoin library.tbl_borrower)natural join library.tbl_book)
WHERE branchName = 'Sharpstown' and date(dueDate)= '2021-07-07';

4.	For each book that is loaned out from the "Sharpstown" branch and whose DueDate is today, retrieve the book title, the borrower's name, and the borrower's address.
